哦，Fonzy又在做饭了吗?
[MAN]: Oh, is Fonzy cooking again?

197
00:12:58,778 --> 00:13:01,072
我不会就这么站在这里听这家伙说话。
I'm not gonna just stand here and listen to this guy.

198
00:13:01,823 --> 00:13:04,367
你以为你是谁，对我们呼来喝去的?
Who do you think you are, bossing us around?

199
00:13:04,451 --> 00:13:05,619
他是一个上校。
He's a colonel.

200
00:13:06,286 --> 00:13:07,370
中校。
Lieutenant Colonel.

201
00:13:07,787 --> 00:13:08,914
是的,对的。
Yeah, right.

202
00:13:09,289 --> 00:13:10,999
“上校”，加上引号。
"Colonel", with air quotes.

203
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:13,502
看到了吗?空气引号。
See? Air quotes.

204
00:13:13,585 --> 00:13:15,462
(泰勒):嗨。嘿。这是怎么回事?
[TAYLOR]: Hey. Hey. What's going on in here?

205
00:13:16,546 --> 00:13:19,090
为什么食物都出来了，福兹?——我饿了。
And why is the food out, Fonzy? - I'm hungry.

206
00:13:19,716 --> 00:13:20,759
你是个吃货。
You're a stress eater.

207
00:13:20,842 --> 00:13:22,219
是啊，别以为我们不知道
Yeah, and don't think we don't know

208
00:13:22,302 --> 00:13:23,678
你一直在房间里做饭。
you've been cooking in your room.

209
00:13:24,513 --> 00:13:25,680
是的。所以呢?
Yeah. So?

210
00:13:26,932 --> 00:13:28,308
你也有愤怒的问题。
You have anger issues, too.

211
00:13:28,391 --> 00:13:29,559
是的,但是……
Yeah, but...

212
00:13:30,352 --> 00:13:32,354
(他叹了口气)我正在努力。
[HE SIGHS] I'm working on it.

213
00:13:34,231 --> 00:13:35,607
你得告诉这个叫T的家伙
You gotta tell this guy, T

214
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:37,400
有辆货车来接我们。
we got a van coming to pick us up.

215
