It's too dangerous to go out there anyway.

219
00:13:46,451 --> 00:13:48,161
听着，如果你有意见的话
Look, if you have a problem with it

220
00:13:48,245 --> 00:13:49,871
你可以去找当局。
you can take it up with the authorities.

221
00:13:50,664 --> 00:13:53,875
你想让我们留在这里被炸成碎片吗?
You want us to stay here and get blown to smithereens?

222
00:13:54,918 --> 00:13:56,127
你告诉他，T。
You tell him, T.

223
00:13:58,380 --> 00:14:00,924
事实上，每个人
Well, the truth is, everyone

224
00:14:01,007 --> 00:14:02,801
我不确定疏散车来了。
I'm not sure the evacuation van's coming.

225
00:14:02,884 --> 00:14:05,262
哦,上帝。——(重叠的声音)
Oh, good Lord. - [OVERLAPPING VOICES]

226
00:14:05,345 --> 00:14:07,889
坚持住!等等,每一个人。等一等。
Hold on! Hold on, everyone. Hold on.

227
