你确定你听说的避难所就是这个吗?
Are you sure that's what you heard about shelter in place?

228
00:14:11,226 --> 00:14:13,728
没错，警长莱特迈尔开了个新闻发布会
Yeah, Sheriff Rightmire held a press conference

229
