我们不能离开。
We're not to leave.

232
00:14:19,776 --> 00:14:21,403
大家都听说过吗?
Is that what everyone heard?

233
00:14:22,070 --> 00:14:23,238
我听到它。
I heard it.

234
00:14:23,822 --> 00:14:24,906
我也听到了。
I heard it, too.

235
00:14:26,032 --> 00:14:27,033
好的。好吧。
OK. Alright.

236
00:14:27,117 --> 00:14:28,994
好吧，这就是避难所。——(ARTHUR):哦。
Well, shelter in place it is. - [ARTHUR]: Oh.

237
00:14:29,077 --> 00:14:31,788
现在让大家都回自己的房间，好吗?
Let's get everyone back to their rooms for now, OK?

238
00:14:31,871 --> 00:14:34,499
我觉得她看起来不太好。
Mm. She don't look good to me.

239
00:14:34,583 --> 00:14:35,875
累了。
Tired.

240
00:14:35,959 --> 00:14:38,587
我去把蜡烛拿出来，以防停电。
I'll get the candles out in case the power goes out.

241
00:14:40,088 --> 00:14:42,090
它会浪漫。呃,罗西?
It'll be romantic. Eh, Rosie?

242
00:14:43,174 --> 00:14:45,260
你把蜡烛留给自己吧。
You keep your candles to yourself.

243
00:14:46,177 --> 00:14:47,971
[男人笑]-[罗丝]:嗯。
[MEN CHUCKLE] - [ROSE]: Mm.

244
