How do you always stay so calm in all of this?

266
00:16:09,761 --> 00:16:10,679
(她笑)
[SHE CHUCKLES]

267
00:16:10,762 --> 00:16:13,014
我经历过几次风暴。
I've been through a few storms before.

268
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,642
它会很好的。——(打雷)
It'll be alright. - [THUNDER CRASHES]

269
00:16:16,434 --> 00:16:18,228
好吧……——(她嗡嗡)
Alright... - [SHE HUMS]

270
00:16:19,145 --> 00:16:21,815
如果停电了，显示器有备用电池
If the power goes out, the monitor has a backup battery

271
00:16:21,898 --> 00:16:22,774
这样就……
and that'll...

272
00:16:22,857 --> 00:16:25,026
这会起作用的，好吗?所以，就让它开着吧。
That'll kick in, OK? So, just leave that on.

273
00:16:25,568 --> 00:16:28,947
没有那东西我怎么活了93年?
How did I live 93 years without that thing?

274
00:16:29,030 --> 00:16:30,573
(他们轻声地笑起来)
[THEY CHUCKLE]

275
00:16:30,657 --> 00:16:33,493
这不是让我心跳的原因，亲爱的。
That's not what's keeping my heart going, honey.

276
00:16:33,576 --> 00:16:35,620
是的,嗯…——(她笑)
Yeah, well... - [SHE CHUCKLES]

277
00:16:37,789 --> 00:16:41,292
我知道现在很艰难。
I know it's hard times here right now.

278
00:16:42,085 --> 00:16:44,587
(她会说西班牙语)
[SHE SPEAKS SPANISH]

279
00:16:46,464 --> 00:16:50,301
不要担心你的生活，你要吃什么或喝什么。
Don't worry about your life, what you will eat or drink.

280
00:16:51,094 --> 00:16:53,221
看天上的鸟。
Look at the birds of the air.

281
00:16:53,304 --> 00:16:55,181
他们不播种也不收获
They neither sow nor reap

282
00:16:55,807 --> 00:16:58,184
然而，你的天父养活了他们。
and yet, your heavenly Father feeds them.

283
00:16:59,811 --> 00:17:00,854
别担心。
Don't worry.

284
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,690
他会提供。
He'll provide.

285
00:17:04,691 --> 00:17:06,067
(打雷)
[THUNDER CRASHES]

286
00:17:06,943 --> 00:17:08,445
我希望我能相信。
I wish I could believe that.

287
00:17:09,028 --> 00:17:12,157
(她轻笑)你会的。就像你父亲一样。
[SHE CHUCKLES] You will. Just like your father.

288
00:17:18,329 --> 00:17:20,415
需要我扶你回到床上吗?
Do you want me to help you get back into bed?

289
00:17:20,498 --> 00:17:21,666
不。我很好。
No. I'm fine.

290
00:17:25,044 --> 00:17:26,212
(泰勒叹了口气)
[TAYLOR SIGHS]

291
00:17:27,422 --> 00:17:30,967
[隆隆雷声]-[倾盆大雨]
[LOUD THUNDER RUMBLES] - [HEAVY RAIN POURS]

