00:19:03,476 --> 00:19:05,186
不。去坐下。
No. Go sit down.

302
00:19:05,645 --> 00:19:07,647
(遥远的风的咆哮)
[DISTANT WIND HOWLS]

303
00:19:08,773 --> 00:19:11,442
(泰勒哼了一声)-哦，让我来帮你。
[TAYLOR GRUNTS] - Oh, let me help you with that.

304
00:19:13,027 --> 00:19:13,987
对不起。
Sorry.

305
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:16,239
他们想在一起。很难拒绝。
They wanted to be together. It's hard to say no.

306
00:19:18,199 --> 00:19:20,410
尽管严格来说，泰勒是对的。
Although, technically, Taylor's right.

307
00:19:20,493 --> 00:19:22,745
联邦应急管理局建议人们呆在室内
FEMA recommends staying in interior rooms

308
00:19:22,829 --> 00:19:24,205
在这种情况下。
in situations like this.

309
00:19:24,914 --> 00:19:26,124
无论如何,书呆子。
Whatever, nerd.

310
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:30,962
我只是说，如果我们都被埋在废墟里可别怪我。
I'm just saying, don't blame me if we all get buried in debris.

311
00:19:31,379 --> 00:19:32,714
哦,亚瑟!
Oh, Arthur!

312
00:19:34,883 --> 00:19:35,967
把它们都拿走。
Just take them all.

313
00:19:36,926 --> 00:19:38,511
让我们从痛苦中解脱出来。
Put us all out of our misery.

314
00:19:39,262 --> 00:19:41,347
哦,不。今天是星期二。
Oh, no. Today's Tuesday only.

315
00:19:41,431 --> 00:19:44,809
