[KNOCK ON DOOR]

321
00:20:04,037 --> 00:20:06,289
(雷声裂缝)
[THUNDER CRACKS]

322
00:20:14,589 --> 00:20:15,798
DEA。
DEA.

323
00:20:15,882 --> 00:20:17,717
我们能进来吗?需要帮助。
Can we come in, please? Need help.

324
00:20:24,849 --> 00:20:26,184
进来吧，亲爱的。
