325
00:20:32,065 --> 00:20:33,399
班纳特科尔,DEA。
Cole Bennett, DEA.

326
00:20:33,483 --> 00:20:35,985
你好，我是泰勒·沃德。我是这里的老板。
Hi, I'm Taylor Ward. I'm the owner of this place.

327
00:20:37,612 --> 00:20:39,155
