What happened? Is he hurt?

328
00:20:40,698 --> 00:20:41,866
这里是医疗机构吗?
Is this is a medical facility?

329
00:20:42,533 --> 00:20:44,702
辅助生活。-[琳达]:怎么了?
Assisted living. - [LINDA]: What's going on?

330
00:20:45,495 --> 00:20:47,830
琳达，你能给他们拿几条毛巾吗?
[TAYLOR]: Linda, can you please grab them some towels?

331
00:20:49,207 --> 00:20:52,418
你们这里有医生吗?-我是护士。没有医生,没有。
