There's a FEMA command post about eight blocks away.

336
00:21:03,429 --> 00:21:04,389
电话没电了。
The phones are dead.

337
00:21:04,472 --> 00:21:06,057
我得步行过去。
I've gotta make it there on foot.

338
00:21:07,016 --> 00:21:08,267
我可以把它们交给你保管吗?
Can I leave them in your care?

339
00:21:11,229 --> 00:21:14,399
女士吗?-是的。当然,是的。是的。
Ma'am? - Yeah. Of course, yes. Yes.

340
00:21:14,482 --> 00:21:15,942
泰勒，怎么了?
Taylor, what's going on?

341
00:21:16,025 --> 00:21:19,362
能帮我准备一下203房吗?我们把它们放在这里。
Can you prep room 203, please? We'll put them up there.

342
00:21:19,445 --> 00:21:20,571
你会没事的。
[COLE]: You'll be OK.

343
00:21:21,197 --> 00:21:23,241
我说过了，我们是养老院的。我不是…
Like I said, we're assisted living. I'm not...

344
00:21:23,324 --> 00:21:25,284
我不确定我能帮上什么忙，但我会尽我所能。
I'm not sure I can help but I'll do whatever I can.

345
00:21:25,868 --> 00:21:28,037
很感激。你在这儿会没事的。
Appreciate it. You'll be alright here.

346
00:21:28,121 --> 00:21:29,205
照顾好你的父亲。
Take care of your father.

347
00:21:33,209 --> 00:21:35,169
