[HE SIGHS] Thank you.

348
00:21:42,885 --> 00:21:43,970
(泰勒叹了口气)
[TAYLOR SIGHS]

349
00:22:03,448 --> 00:22:04,866
快进来吧。
Just come right in here.

350
00:22:06,743 --> 00:22:08,828
好了。(她咕哝声)
